      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies both reliability and sophisticated engineering. This exceptional example has been preserved to a high standard, offering a refined driving experience and a comprehensive service history. Discerning buyers will appreciate the balance of performance and aesthetic integrity, making it a premier choice in its class. We invite you to experience the quality and poise of this well-appointed motorcar.",
