    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as it is fun to drive? I'm parting with my trusty car, and it has been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-maintained, clean, and totally ready for its next adventure! It runs like a dream and has plenty of life left in it. Whether you're commuting or hitting the road for a weekend trip, this beauty won't let you down. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
